title: Woody's Oasis -  MSU Food Court
typeOfFood: Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mediterranean deli with multiple locatinos; this one is inside Michigan State University Crossroads food court. Offers vegan suitable items like mujadara, smeed, baba gannoush, hummus, falafels, rice stuffed grape leaves, tahini, eggplant stew, lentil soup, and most of the vegetarian sandwiches are vegan except for the Labanee (Syrian cheese).
